"{\n  \"text\": \"You don't need to eat a lot of fermented foods. You need to eat them regularly. Just a couple bites, a couple of times a day does the trick. This is powerful food. It's full of bacteria, beneficial bacteria that helps balance your gut's bacteria. It helps regrow your gut's bacteria. In fact, if you're first starting to eat fermented foods, you want to make sure not to eat a lot of it all at once because you may get what's called die-off symptoms. This bacteria and just your regular fermented foods will hunt out the bad pathogenic bacteria in your gut. And as it kills this bad bacteria, that bacteria will release toxins, which can equate to gas, bloating, and general discomfort. It's not a problem. It's balancing your gut, but you want to eat a little bit less if you do experience these die-off symptoms. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" You don't need to eat a lot of fermented foods.\",\n      \"start\": 1.6,\n      \"end\": 4.64,\n      \"duration\": 3.04,\n      \"confidence\": 0.995,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" You\",\n          \"start\": 1.6,\n          \"end\": 1.92,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.997\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" don\",\n          \"start\": 1.92,\n          \"end\": 2.16,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"'\",\n          \"start\": 2.16,\n          \"end\": 2.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"t\",\n          \"start\": 2.4,\n          \"end\": 2.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.0,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" need\",\n          \"start\": 2.4,\n          \"end\": 2.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" to\",\n          \"start\": 2.64,\n          \"end\"